    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n……何を見ているんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ good work today.\n…What are you looking at?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4333333254,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2000.0000079000001,
          "startTime": 5.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "結婚式場のパンフレットだよ。今度お世話になるから\nどんな場所か調べておこうと思ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A wedding venue pamphlet. We'll be working there soon.\nI thought I’d look into what kind of place it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが結婚式場のお世話に！？\nあ、あの……それは誰と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re visiting a wedding venue!?\nU-Um… with whom…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.211481921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰って、一緒に行く相手は怜に決まってるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean \"with whom\"? My partner is obviously you‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4405448197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね、相手は私……私！？\nこ、これって、もしかして……プロポーズ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so your partner is me… ME!?\nI-Is this… a proposal…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.788633148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って下さい\n急に言われても心の準備が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ just a moment!\nEven if you say it so suddenly‚ I’m not mentally prepared…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4219664813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？　なんだか様子が変だぞ\n怜は……嫌なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong? You’re acting strange.\nDo you… not want to‚ Rei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "嫌というか、突然のことで混乱してしまって……\n{user}さんと、け、けけ、結婚……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that I don't want to‚ it’s just so sudden I’m confused…\nG-G-G-Getting married to {user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3404101929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、怜が嫌なら仕方ない……\n分かった、この仕事は俺の方から断っておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. If you don't want to‚ I can't force you…\nOkay‚ I'll turn down this job then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、いきなり言われても困りま……\nえ？　今、仕事って言いました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you say that so suddenly‚ it’s troubl…\nWait. Did you just say \"job\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7131168288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。星見市にある結婚式場のCMに、怜が\nウエディングドレスで出演する……言ってなかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Rei‚ you're going to appear in a commercial for a venue in Hoshimi\nwearing a wedding dress… Did I not tell you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてません！　それを先に言って下さい！\n変な勘違いをしちゃったじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't heard that! Tell me those things first!\nYou made me have a strange misunderstanding!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.182694046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "勘違い？\nもしかして、俺と結婚すると思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Misunderstanding?\nNo way‚ did you think you were getting married to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います！\n私と{user}さんが結婚なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ that's not it!\nMe and {user} getting married…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.96294752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな勘違いする人、いる訳ないじゃないですか！\nそんな勘違い、絶対に誰もしませんから！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way anyone would misunderstand like that!\nNo one would EVER think that‚ absolutely nobody!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.26294752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Day of the CM shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3592765252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5926103671
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5926103671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "今日はここで撮影をするんですね\n素敵な結婚式場ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So today's shoot is happening here.\nIt's a wonderful wedding venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0296091005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9791103125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もしかして今\n「怜でも結婚式に憧れるのか」って思いました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ were you just thinking\n\"Even Rei dreams of a wedding\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7629424338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.6489365339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですね、私だって女の子なんですよ\n結婚式やウエディングドレスに憧れくらいあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How rude. I'm a girl too‚ you know.\nI have dreams about weddings and wedding dresses too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2962686464,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.671506500009,
          "startTime": 127.4629401529
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.0172696192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "念押しされなくても、ちゃんと分かってるって……\nおや？　今、カメラのシャッター音が聞こえたぞ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it even if you don't insist…\nHuh? Was that a camera shutter sound just now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あそこにいる女の子、俺達にスマホのカメラを\n向けているぞ！　まさか、怜を盗撮しているんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That girl over there is pointing her smartphone camera\nright at us! Is she taking photos of you secretly…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.5668778498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "違いますよ。彼女は私の同級生です\nさっきロビーで偶然会って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ she's my classmate.\nWe happened to run into each other in the lobby…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7749181355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "これからウエディングドレスを着るんだって話したら\n凄く驚いて、羨ましがられました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told her I was going to wear a wedding dress‚\nshe was very surprised and envious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3082514689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.9157320737
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.6415848022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "友達同士で写真を撮り合うのは変じゃないでしょう？\nほら、{user}さんも手を振って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not weird for friends to take photos of each other‚ right?\nCome on‚ {user}‚ wave to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8415848022,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6622.529321299993,
          "startTime": 159.538261395
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7055.672092399987,
          "startTime": 159.9714041661
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……\nでも、怜の同級生がどうして結婚式場に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nBut why is your classmate at a wedding venue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.254079604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんが結婚するので\n付き添いで式場を下見に来たそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her older sister is getting married‚\nso she came to check out the venue with her.",
