      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんの下見に付き添うなんて\n姉妹仲がいいですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Accompanying her sister to a venue viewing‚\nthey must be very close sisters.",
