      "text": "兄は恥ずかしがって\nそういうことは全然話してくれないので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My brother is shy‚\nso he never tells me things like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
